videos.headline: Prukop throws 77-yard TD under pressure
videos.description: Oregon QB Dakota Prukop tosses a 77-yard rocket to Devon Allen in the third quarter to extend the Ducks' lead to 37-13 over Virginia.

videos.headline: Freeman puts on the jets to extend Ducks' lead
videos.description: Oregon's Royce Freeman records his 18th 100-yard rushing game since the start of 2014. He continues his streak with this 85-yard rushing touchdown in the fourth quarter of play against Virginia.
